author: Matthew Facciani
title: 250,000 More People Attend Women’s March Than Trump’s Inauguration
text:
— Malena Ernman (@Malena_Ernman) January 21, 2017 Donald Trump is so unpopular that there are even women marching against him in Antarctica. Picture: Linda Zunas #WomensMarch pic.twitter.com/CXWx67UUmJ 
— Lynzy Billing (@LynzyBilling) January 21, 2017 
Trump may have barely won the election, but there are many people in our country and around the world who will be fighting him every step of the way. Keep up with my writing, activism, and research by following me on Facebook!
